column2: "So the real culprit was hiding in plain sight all along... Come on, if it was a gift, he should have given it to the real one! What was he thinking!"
"Um... It was certainly a surprise, but at least the mystery's solved now. Let's use the rest of our Halloween to have fun!"
"Oh, yes, that's right. An enemy repulsion mission was posted near the Halloween event venue."
"Alright, then it's settled! Halloween Witch Magical★Xiera will beat all the naughty children black and blue☆"
